T1: Snapshot writes data up to timestamp T0
T2: Worker deletes current.wal
T3: Metric arrives with timestamp T0+100ms
T4: Metric written to current.wal
T5: Process crashes
T6: On restart: Snapshot from T0 + empty WAL
T7: Data from T0+100ms is lost!
```

