## BUG #4: SILENT DATA LOSS ON BACKPRESSURE

### The Issue

```
Channel size = 65536 / walNumShards
With 4 workers: 65536 / 4 = 16384 per shard
At 100k msg/sec across 4 workers: 25k msg/sec per shard
Channel fills in: 16384 / 25000 = 0.65 seconds
```

Every drop violates the durability guarantee, but drops are only logged every 10k drops.

### Fix Strategy: Implement Real Backpressure

```go
// In lineprotocol.go DecodeLine:
